Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Another peaceful day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How right you are, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This room is... the picture of peace for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup, Kirie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stop barging into my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And that room... is the picture of HELL for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish things could stay like this forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today... I'LL be your girlfriend, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought this on the way over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that adventure game everyone's been talking about:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"My Younger Sister is My Girlfriend (BOOM!)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, "YoungBOOM!" for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Sensei. Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sensei"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is my friend, Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,F-f-friend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Alex. He works with my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure. Please, call me "Alex."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,DAZZLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You stood in line for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Is this girl the main heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,YoungBOOM! has a famous voice actress for each
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the younger sister roles, so there is no "main."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However! This character, Hikari, is based on the famous\Nactor Hikaru Kongo, who's really popular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, naturally, she's become a favorite character.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already started selling merchandise\Nfor this character online.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! We've got some options!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... B, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I guess that would be all right.\NBut only to the school gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, people will think will that we're classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better than on her last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She does a good job\Nof not sounding too lovey-dovey, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I can't keep up\Nwith what they're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm the only one who\Ncan't follow the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have the Master scolding me for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There she is, in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... this is a tough one, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we should go with "C."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These types tend to be shy, so I doubt\Nthey'd enjoy being spoken to at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"SHY"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Motoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Her gaze is as sharp as ever, huh?\NAh! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her gaze is as sharp as ever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Motoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... "A" would be a good choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"A - Talk to her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In my experience, that makes your\NFavorability Rating go down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-in any case, pretending you didn't see her\Nis out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So... shall we save the game and try both options?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... s-sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... c'mon, don't talk to me at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough's enough. You can't just ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka-poww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Motoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always spending time\Nwith my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Motoba... you want to go home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y... y-y... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you buy a new game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Chomp Chomp Watching"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've heard of that.\NThey're always running commercials for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp! Watching 'em chomp and chomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp! Chomp, chomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta keep up with the new trends,\Nso I've had my eye on this for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This game is for kids, so I can finish it by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to take breaks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already gotten the hang of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure does have a lot of side quests...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ho... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, you're still playing that game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't find any of the super rare items...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes look straight-up DEAD!\NHow long have you been playing that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... about 10 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, she had the same look when\Nshe played that social-network game for an entire day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she gets into it, she just can't stop, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she'll probably get tired of it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! This week's JUMPU is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play games while you're eating!\NAnd you're using the touch pen to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out already! GET OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like more and more people\Nare playing this game way too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex! This isn't good at all! It's already 10:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I just couldn't find any super rare items...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-this game is bad news.\NI have to do something, and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A way to make someone... quit the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. One of our junior workers is playing it too much,\Nand it's gotten me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, this is about Umaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really play games,\Nso I don't know that much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't play them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Still, if there's something I really like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I won't be able to stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no help at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru! I bought a game too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ready to hop on the big wave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play co-op!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But we've only been playing for an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When a game's as fun as this,\Nit's a shame to play too much at once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to enjoy it a little at a time. Well, time to make lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When she likes something, she just can't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll teach her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to TRULY enjoy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This super rare item...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our collection's complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure was a long road getting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These modern games have gotten pretty tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now she'll have gotten over\NChomp Chomp Watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone out there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a big announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chomp Chomp Watching 2" will be going on sale soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, there will be different versions:\NTruffle, Foie Gras, and Caviar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With that horn, there's no doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei the Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Taihei was back in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what the heck? That was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was exaggerated a little but it wasn't a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a test-taking demon who always got 100s,\Nso they called him Taihei the Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They called you that all the time.\NLike, even when you met Kanau...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough talk about the past.\NI'm gonna get dinner ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Big Brother mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, he's a good guy.\NHe wouldn't get mad over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taihei wouldn't yell or do something half-cocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he'll scold you,\Nbut he doesn't actually get MAD, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, Umaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat your vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Umaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! But he can get super cranky\Nif you bug him when he's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Tanukichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like to see Ebina again.\NDoes she not come over often?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why Ebina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You wanna hear, Tanukichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina is SUPER kind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I started thinking, a girl like that\Ncould make friends with my sister for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis always has a scary look on her face,\Nso I don't think she has many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina doesn't seem like the type\Nwho'd worry about that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good guy, Bomba! Ebina would-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?! Like, what's "good"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I often think to myself, "Self, you ARE a good guy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I think the area around my eyes TOTALLY\Nmakes me look like a good guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You really get me, Tanukichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are getting worked up...\NYou're in for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are getting worked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Metal Nyankosu - Metal Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomba takes 105 points damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pew, pew, pew! Bomba is almost out of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's raining! I have to bring the laundry in!\NPew, pew, pew! Bomba is almost out of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's raining! I have to bring the laundry in!\NMetal Nyankosu merely shakes its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Metal Nyankosu merely shakes its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go get it. So stay out of the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, and these were almost dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's taste test!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear, all clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear, all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear, all clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear, all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,HANDS OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Taihei the Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,L-look, we're sorry for barging in here, but you're getting\Na bit TOO angry. What's going on, Taihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the lid on just in case when I stepped away\Nfrom the stove, but I didn't make myself clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was heating up oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 20 years I've known you,\Nthat was the first time I've seen you get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Twenty years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit lying. It's been more like 10, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirie! Let's hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I hope you're well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kirie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Cold and Bristly Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she doesn't look too happy...\NWait, "bristly"? Like, thorny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she only seems to go from cold to painfully rude,\Nso: Cold and Bristly Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that's some nice naming, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I'm following any of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold and Bristly Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the timing couldn't be better.\NI brought a present with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Italian cat figurine.\NI gave one to your brother as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Metal Nyankosu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You've had this customized\Nall nice and cute, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have this one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what is this present for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my way of thanking you\Nfor all you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is for you, Cold and Bristly Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want this, but I totally accepted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this is the first time I've gotten\Na present from someone who wasn't a family member...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Damage version of Madam Black Death Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Damage powers make her\Nalready-erotic clothing even MORE erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, I'm so glad that this made you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I was surprised by your choice\Nin that game we played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never dreamed someone could\Nbeat me at a girl's game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my all-time favorite figurine.\NIt's only right that you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make me happy at all! And I don't know\Nhow to react when getting a present I don't want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd get THIS happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure lucked out, huh, Kirie?\NAlso, this thing is really well made!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only buy it at anime events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'll give it to my Master!\NIf it's mine, it should be all right to give it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have something so LEWD\Ngo anywhere near my Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're all free, we'll be having a Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas has no place in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? C'mon, give us SOMETHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kirie! When is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy you a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this cake is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Cold and Bristly Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure lucked out, huh, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure lucked out, huh, Kirie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU SURE LUCKED OUT, HUH, KIRIE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: German for "Every rose has its thorn."\NKeine Rose Ohne Dornen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you crave it, there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, your burger combo meal\Ncomes with CRISPY NUGGETS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M LOVING... HAMBURGERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do they get off using a commercial like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want a hamburger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure feels like winter now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um, here's a picture from when\Nwe went to the movies the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to go somewhere\Nduring our winter vacation, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anywhere you want to go, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I said it without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shwburger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How right you are! Mention hamburgers,\Nand of course that means GERMANY!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, you mentioned in your class introduction\Nthat you're from Germany, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Umaru, how kind of you to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! Let's all go feast on Japanese hamburgers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've never been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one place you can NOT go to\Nunless you're with friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's proceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sylphin! Which should we choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend one of the combo meals, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once you crave it, there's no going back."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'M LOVING HAMBURGERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This convenience store burger and fries\Ngo great with cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard going out to eat all alone,\Nso having it at home is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Umaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-do you not like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, this feels\Nlike a high school girl experience, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So... good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Ebina, are you going to eat all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one has about 500 calories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I-I'll freeze them!\NI was going to freeze them when I got home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all eat before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, these taste best when they're freshly made!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei! It seems we'll be doing\Nthis next episode preview together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine and all, but why do you\Nkeep calling me "Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sign of respect! But I could call you Wise One,\Nor Master, or Your Majesty, or Honored Husband -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Those last two seem sort of different...
